1. They're mostly downtrodden or depressed, with not much hope for the future, but they seem to see that the Roosevelts have the power to change that.
2. They're asking for ways to earn money or work, seemingly grasping at straws or hoping that the Roosevelts have an option. They're not asking for handouts or free money.
3. They seem to have a pretty positive opinion, thinking that the Roosevelts are sincere and actually interested in the welfare of the people in general.
